{"type": "article", "id": 12257, "title": "可以画画的太阳聚光镜", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-17T11:00:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000230aAmjzrvcgQbMslUL.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t意大利设计师 Rosalia Galeano，Francesca Padoyan 和 Paola Papetti 合作推出了一款可以画画的太阳聚光镜 “Febo”，它有一个木制的底盘和一个放大镜组成，利用放大镜将太阳光线集中，温度升高后在木制底盘随心雕刻，上面留下属于自己的印记。除此之外，它还可以在皮质材料，纤维材料等上面雕刻，让物品充满个人特色。目前产品正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，售价 29 美元，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/maumau/febo\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140030QDYqkNAjIHCU31xr.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"329\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.48382353\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140030U7vLJomyIxGCTd34.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"510\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140031Ep402ZagMxnYXGKI.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"507\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.74558824\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140032JGnxjbuNZBeL8lcX.jpg\" width=\"679\" height=\"252\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.37113402\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140032TpeN9gRF6jrMatmC.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"510\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140033rxXqzy75lvPZ9NGF.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"510\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140033TRDuyWYJ3BMc5870.jpg\" width=\"680